Thornbed
----------

Thornbed is a simple oEmbed wrapper to help you get metadata from different services

It currently supports imgur, youtube, flickr, quickmeme, vimeo

It is very easy to add new services to it, since it uses oEmbed lib

And even you can add a service that doesn't provide oEmbed suppert like imgur, quickmeme, etc...

Getting started
---------------

1. Download and install this package.

2. use it::

    import thornbed

    res = thornbed.embed('http://youtu.be/a1Y73sPHKxw')

3. Have fun !


